ygData.messageBody:
Well here is some advice on where to hunt for DE
(this might not work for you btw). lvl 1-4 nektulos
forest. 4-7-East Commons can get factions w/FP by killing
orcs. 7-10 Orcs in Sro-(always open)10-14 Dervs in Nro
& Sro (sro dervs always open hehe)15-18-orc highway
in oasis, or sirens in OOT,18-22 Aviaks in Lake
Rathe, Nenja.22-30 Treants in South Karana, bad faction
hit but lost of money hehe, 30-35 Cazic thule,
Dwarves in OOT & the wood elves on dock, 35-50 lower guk,
sol A, Sol B or Specs in Ferrott, Barbarians in West
Karana, Guards in Gnome newbie zone, Ice Giants in that
cold place by halas...ect. Only bad faction u get is
for those in killing treants rest faction stay the
same for the city & FP guards love ya, Trolls still
like ya, Ogers Still like ya even Dwarves like ya if u
don't kill the Dwarves in OOT ect..depends all on your
type of playin gI got lvl 40 in 5 months but messed
around alot so..have fun hehe.
